&lt;p&gt;For further information on this secondment please contact Samantha Jaques-Newton, Head of Allied Health Care Professions and Practice Development Samantha.Jaques-Newton1@nhs.net or Sadie Milner Quality Standards Practice Development Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
